            <td align="center" colspan=2><font color="#000000" style="font-size: 22px"><strong>福州某醫院稱看病滿2000元就送火車票</strong></font></td></tr>
            
          <tr><td align=center colspan=2><br><font style="font-size:14px">http://www.chinareviewnews.com</font>
             &nbsp;&nbsp;2012-01-09 10:52:51&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
